{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Lion introduces Resume:a simpler way for apps to exit and later resume where they left off. Come learn how to take advantage of new APIs to enable your users to spend less time managing your app and more time using it. You will learn about the Resume feature as we walk through converting real applications to adopt automatic termination and window restoration. The session will include plenty of concrete code samples and practical advice."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-119-resume-and-automatic-termination-in-lion"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-119-Resume-and-Automatic-Termination-in-Lion","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Resume and Automatic Termination in Lion"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/119\/","overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","type":"reference","isActive":true},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC11":{"title":"WWDC11","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentatio